{
  "stem": "19895.3",
  "chunk_idx": 2,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 63.5,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "And it was a time when we knew about how anti-Jewish laws and-- and-- and-- and atrocities in these surrounding countries were already advanced more than against the Hungarian Jews, which historically speaking, has held out till probably the very last time of the Final Solution of Hitler, where he wanted to eliminate all of the Jews of-- of the world, of Europe, first of all.",
      "word_count": 66
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "And-- and The Final Solution became [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] very traumatic.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "And-- and its final days in Hungary came later than the surrounding countries.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "But then, boy, did it ever.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "Because most of the Auschwitz late arrivers were Hungarian Jews from the countryside and last, from Budapest, the major capital.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "And interestingly, Budapest Jews, unless you were in the-- in the leading of the Jewish community, knew very little about-- that the country Jews were already deported and taken away to extermination camps and concentration camps.",
      "word_count": 36
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "And we always hoped that it will never happen in Hungary.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "And then we never will have to go through on anything with Budapest.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "We were not able to make contacts by writing to our relatives who lived in the countryside.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "We didn't know what happened.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "But nobody answered anymore to our letters.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And communications by telephone, it was rather unknown there was telephone in the country.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "But very few of the private homes of our type of people had telephones those days.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And you couldn't get one if you asked for one, because it was given only to people who they wanted to have telephones.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And we couldn't just call on the telephone, because not every home had a telephone like nowadays.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "It's expected that everybody has a phone, at least one.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I wanted to grow up, get an education.",
      "word_count": 8
    }
  ],
